<item>
            <title>[OPENJPA-970] SchemaToolTask does not have &quot;dropTables&quot; argument</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-970</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The task SchemaToolTask does not implements&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;dropTables&quot; argument. According to the documentation &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; this task can&lt;br/&gt;
take &quot;dropTables&quot; arguments&lt;br/&gt;
but when I run as shown below I get this error: The &amp;lt;schematool&amp;gt; type&lt;br/&gt;
doesn&apos;t support the &quot;droptables&quot; attribute.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;lt;schematool dropTables=&quot;false&quot; action=&quot;refresh&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;fileset dir=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{build.sql.dir}
&lt;p&gt;&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;include name=&quot;schema.xml&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/fileset&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;config&lt;br/&gt;
propertiesFile=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{prototype.src.model.base}
&lt;p&gt;/META-INF/persistence.xml&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/schematool&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In fact, I looked in source code and this task has no set method for&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;dropTables&quot;argument.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I use :&lt;br/&gt;
revision.number=422266:683325&lt;br/&gt;
openjpa.version=1.2.0&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://openjpa.apache.org/builds/1.2.0/apache-openjpa-1.2.0/docs/manual/ref_guide_schema_schematool.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://openjpa.apache.org/builds/1.2.0/apache-openjpa-1.2.0/docs/manual/ref_guide_schema_schematool.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks, &lt;/p&gt;</description>
